#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investments"
msgstr "Naložbe"

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investments in &kmymoney;"
msgstr "Naložbe v &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In very general terms, an <emphasis>investment</emphasis> is any allocation "
"of money with the expectation of a future benefit. &kmymoney;'s Investment "
"accounts are designed for one particular type of investment: securities. A "
"security investment (or just a security) is an instrument for investing "
"money that is traded on a market with the intention of a profitable return "
"in the form of either appreciation in value, income such as interest or "
"dividends, or a combination of both. Stocks and mutual funds are the most "
"common securities; and they are the ones specifically supported within "
"&kmymoney;. Bonds have a different financial structure, but can usually be "
"handled by &kmymoney;. Futures, commodities, options, and more complex "
"investment instruments like derivatives are other types of investments, but "
"&kmymoney; has no special functionality for them. As long an investment has "
"similar characteristics to a stock or mutual fund, it can be tracked."
msgstr ""
"V zelo splošnem smislu je <emphasis>naložba</emphasis> vsaka dodelitev "
"denarja s pričakovanjem prihodnje koristi. Naložbeni računi &kmymoney; so "
"zasnovani za eno posebno vrsto naložb: vrednostne papirje. Naložba v "
"vrednostni papir (ali samo vrednostni papir) je instrument za vlaganje "
"denarja, s katerim se trguje na trgu z namenom dobičkonosnega donosa v "
"obliki povečanja vrednosti, dohodka, kot so obresti ali dividende, ali "
"kombinacije obojega. Delnice in vzajemni skladi so najpogostejši vrednostni "
"papirji; in so tisti, ki so posebej podprti v &kmymoney;. Obveznice imajo "
"drugačno finančno strukturo, vendar jih običajno lahko upravlja &kmymoney;. "
"Terminske pogodbe, blago, opcije in bolj zapleteni naložbeni instrumenti, "
"kot so izvedeni finančni instrumenti, so druge vrste naložb, vendar "
"&kmymoney; zanje nima posebnih funkcionalnosti. Dokler ima naložba podobne "
"lastnosti kot delnica ali vzajemni sklad, ji je mogoče slediti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment Accounts"
msgstr "Naložbeni računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A &kmymoney; Investment Account holds a collection of Securities, also "
"referred to as Equities. An Investment account contains transactions, "
"recording activities such as buys, sells, dividends, reinvestments, yields, "
"splits and income of those investments. Each transaction in an Investment "
"account must relate to a specific security."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; naložbeni račun vsebuje zbirko vrednostnih papirjev, imenovanih "
"tudi delnice. Naložbeni račun vsebuje transakcije, beleženje dejavnosti, kot "
"so nakupi, prodaje, dividende, ponovne naložbe, donosi, delitve in prihodki "
"teh naložb. Vsaka transakcija na naložbenem računu se mora nanašati na "
"določen vrednostni papir."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is common for an account at a Brokerage Institution to contain both "
"securities and cash. In &kmymoney;, an Investment account holds "
"<emphasis>only</emphasis> securities. It cannot contain any cash balance. "
"This was a design decision made when Investment accounts were first included "
"in &kmymoney;. It might be changed in the future, but that is likely to be "
"done as part of a significant revision in all of &kmymoney;'s handling of "
"investments. For now, any cash needed to purchase a security or gained from "
"a sell or dividend transaction requires the use of a Brokerage Account."
msgstr ""
"Običajno je, da račun pri borznoposredniški instituciji vsebuje vrednostne "
"papirje in gotovino. V &kmymoney; ima naložbeni račun <emphasis>samo</"
"emphasis> vrednostne papirje. Ne sme vsebovati stanja gotovine. To je bila "
"odločitev, sprejeta, ko so bili naložbeni računi prvič vključeni v "
"&kmymoney;. Morda bo to v prihodnosti spremenjeno, vendar bo to verjetno "
"storjeno kot del pomembne revizije celotnega ravnanja &kmymoney; z "
"naložbami. Zaenkrat vsa gotovina, ki je potrebna za nakup vrednostnega "
"papirja ali pridobljena s transakcijo prodaje ali dividende, zahteva uporabo "
"posredniškega računa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brokerage Accounts"
msgstr "Borznoposredniški računi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When an investment transaction uses (to buy a security) or produces case, "
"such as from a sale or dividend, that transaction must refer to another "
"account which can hold the money, most commonly a checking account. You can "
"specify any suitable account for any investment transaction which requires "
"one. However, &kmymoney; has the concept of a <emphasis>Brokerage Account</"
"emphasis>, also sometimes referred to as a <quote>Cash Account</quote>, "
"which is the default account for such transactions."
msgstr ""
"Kadar naložbena transakcija uporablja (za nakup vrednostnega papirja) ali se "
"ustvari primer zaradi prodaje ali dividende, se mora ta transakcija nanašati "
"na drug račun na katerem je lahko denar, najpogosteje na tekoči račun. "
"Določite lahko kateri koli ustrezen račun za katero koli naložbeno "
"transakcijo, ki ga potrebuje. Vendar &kmymoney; ima koncept "
"<emphasis>Posredniškega računa</emphasis>, včasih imenovan tudi "
"<quote>Gotovinski račun</quote>, ki je privzeti račun za takšne transakcije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create an Investment Account, you have the option of creating an "
"associated Brokerage Account with it. The default name of the Brokerage "
"account will be the name of the investment account with \" (Brokerage)\" "
"appended. &kmymoney; assumes this naming convention in several actions "
"related to investments. Following the convention is not absolutely required, "
"but without it, you will often have to take extra steps to complete the "
"entry of transactions."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarite naložbeni račun, imate možnost, da z njim ustvarite povezan "
"posredniški račun. Privzeto ime posredniškega računa bo ime naložbenega "
"računa z dodatkom » (Borzno posredovanje)«. &kmymoney; prevzame to "
"konvencijo poimenovanja v več dejanjih, povezanih z naložbami. Sledenje "
"konvenciji ni absolutno obvezno, a brez nje boste pogosto morali izvesti "
"dodatne korake za dokončanje vnosa transakcij."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Base Currency"
msgstr "Osnovna valuta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your &kmymoney; data file has a base currency, specified when the file was "
"created. In addition, an Investment account has a base currency, specified "
"when it is created. Separately, each security has its own base currency. "
"This is the currency in which it is traded. When a price quote is entered "
"for an investment, the currency of the value given is always its base "
"currency. A stock on the NYSE (New York Stock Exchange) would be in US "
"dollars (USD), and one on an Australian market would be in Australian "
"dollars (AUD). The base currency for a security does not need to be the same "
"as the base currency for the Investment account holding that security."
msgstr ""
"Vaša podatkovna datoteka &kmymoney; ima osnovno valuto, določeno ob "
"ustvarjanju datoteke. Poleg tega ima naložbeni račun osnovno valuto, ki je "
"določena ob ustvarjanju. Vsak vrednostni papir ima ločeno svojo osnovno "
"valuto. To je valuta, v kateri se trguje. Ko se za naložbo vnese ponudbena "
"cena, je valuta podane vrednosti vedno njena osnovna valuta. Delnica na NYSE "
"(Newyorška borza) bi bila v ameriških dolarjih (USD), delnica na avstralskem "
"trgu pa v avstralskih dolarjih (AUD). Ni nujno, da je osnovna valuta za "
"vrednostni papir enaka osnovni valuti za naložbeni račun, na katerem je ta "
"vrednostni papir."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Investments View"
msgstr "Pogled naložb"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Investments View provides a summary of all your investments, similar to "
"several of the other major views. It has a single display area, with two "
"tabs. The first tab, <guilabel>Equities</guilabel>, provides a high level "
"view of those securities held within a single Investment Account, as "
"specified in the <guilabel>Select Account:</guilabel> dropdown. The second "
"tab, <guilabel>Securities</guilabel>, is similar, but provides slightly "
"different information about all the stocks, mutual funds, bonds, &etc;, you "
"track in &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Pogled naložb nudi povzetek vseh vaših naložb, podobno kot več drugih "
"glavnih pogledov. Ima eno samo območje prikaza z dvema zavihkoma. Prvi "
"zavihek, <guilabel>Delnice</guilabel>, nudi pogled na visoki ravni tistih "
"vrednostnih papirjev, ki so v enem naložbenem računu, kot je določeno v "
"spustnem meniju <guilabel>Izberi račun:</guilabel>. Drugi zavihek, "
"<guilabel>Vrednostni papirji</guilabel>, je podoben, vendar ponuja nekoliko "
"drugačne informacije o vseh delnicah, vzajemnih skladih, obveznicah itd., ki "
"jim sledite v &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Equities tab"
msgstr "Zavihek lastniškega kapitala"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>investments view equities tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogled naložb, zavihek lastniškega kapitala</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>investments view equities tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogled naložb, zavihek lastniškega kapitala</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The distinction between equities and securities on these two tabs may seem "
"somewhat arbitrary, and is known to cause confusion. Perhaps the terminology "
"may be changed in the future, if anyone can propose a different set of terms "
"that doesn't have the same or other problems. However, as stated above, in "
"the current terminology, an equity as shown on the Equities Tab currently "
"refers to the details of an investment within an investment account. Within "
"&kmymoney;, it is a sub-account of an investment account, denominated in a "
"security. A security as shown on the Securities Tab provides access to the "
"security information unrelated to any account. A security can be referenced "
"in multiple equities, which can also be said as different equities can be "
"denominated in the same security."
msgstr ""
"Razlikovanje med lastniškimi vrednostnimi papirji in vrednostnimi papirji na "
"teh dveh zavihkih se morda zdi nekoliko samovoljno in znano je, da povzroča "
"zmedo. Morda bo terminologija v prihodnosti spremenjena, če lahko kdo "
"predlaga drugačen sklop izrazov, ki nima enakih ali drugih težav. Vendar se, "
"kot je navedeno zgoraj, v trenutni terminologiji lastniški kapital, kot je "
"prikazan na zavihku Delnice, trenutno nanaša na podrobnosti naložbe znotraj "
"naložbenega računa. Znotraj &kmymoney; je podračun investicijskega računa, "
"denominiran v vrednostnem papirju. Vrednostni papir, kot je prikazan na "
"zavihku Vrednostni papirji, omogoča dostop do informacij o vrednostnem "
"papirju, ki niso povezane z nobenim računom. Vrednostni papir se lahko "
"sklicuje na več lastniških vrednostnih papirjev, kar lahko tudi rečemo, da "
"so lahko različni lastniški vrednostni papirji denominirani v istem "
"vrednostnem papirju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of the list of equities is the <guilabel>Select Account:</"
"guilabel> dropdown, where you can select the investment account for which "
"you want to see the specific investments. If you have checked <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.general.views\">Synchronize account selection of Ledgers "
"View and Investments View</link> in the configuration dialog, then if you "
"are looking at an investment account in the Ledgers View, and then switch to "
"the Investments View, that account will already be selected."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu seznama lastniškega kapitala je spustni meni <guilabel>Izberi račun:"
"</guilabel>, kjer lahko izberete naložbeni račun, za katerega želite videti "
"določene naložbe. Če ste v pogovornem oknu konfiguracije označili <link "
"linkend=\"details.settings.general.views\">Sinhroniziraj izbiro računa v "
"pogledu lavne knjige in Pogleda naložb</link>, potem če si ogledujete "
"naložbeni račun v pogledu glavne knjige, in nato preklopite na pogled "
"naložb, bo ta račun že izbran."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the Institutions and several other views, the Equities tab "
"displays several columns with descriptive and summary information about each "
"equity. As with the Institutions View, you can select which columns are "
"shown by right-clicking any column heading and selecting or unselecting the "
"checkbox next to the name of the column."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pri Institucijah in več drugih pogledih, zavihek Lastniški "
"kapital prikazuje več stolpcev z opisnimi in povzetki informacij o vsakem "
"lastniškem kapitalu. Tako kot pri pogledu institucij lahko izberete, kateri "
"stolpci so prikazani, tako da z desno miškino tipko kliknete naslov stolpca "
"in izberete ali počistite potrditveno polje poleg imena stolpca."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the equity. This column is always displayed. All the other "
"columns are optionally display, as described above."
msgstr ""
"Ime lastniškega kapitala. Ta stolpec je vedno prikazan. Vsi drugi stolpci so "
"neobvezno prikazani, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:155 details-investments.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbol"
msgstr "Simbol"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is trading symbol as used on the market where the equity is traded."
msgstr ""
"To je trgovalni simbol, ki se uporablja na trgu, kjer se trguje z delnicami."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quantity"
msgstr "Količina"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the number of shares of the equity you own in this investment "
"account. The precision of this and the other value columns can be adjusted, "
"as described later in this section."
msgstr ""
"To je število delnic lastniškega kapitala, ki ga imate na tem naložbenem "
"računu. Natančnost tega in drugih stolpcev vrednosti je mogoče prilagoditi, "
"kot je opisano kasneje v tem razdelku."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Price"
msgstr "Cena"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the most recent price for this equity known to &kmymoney;."
msgstr "To je zadnja cena za ta lastniški kapital, ki jo pozna &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value"
msgstr "Vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the total value of this investment in this investment account. It "
"should be the same as the product of the Quantity and the Price."
msgstr ""
"To je skupna vrednost te naložbe na tem naložbenem računu. Biti mora enak "
"zmnožku količine in cene."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last Price Update"
msgstr "Zadnja posodobitev cene"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the date of the most recent price. Prices can be updated in several "
"ways, all described later in this section."
msgstr ""
"To je datum zadnje cene. Cene je mogoče posodobiti na več načinov, ki so vsi "
"opisani v nadaljevanju tega razdelka."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The order for any of the columns except Name can be changed by left clicking "
"the column header, and dragging it to the left or right."
msgstr ""
"Vrstni red za kateri koli stolpec, razen za ime, lahko spremenite tako, da "
"levo kliknete glavo stolpca in ga povlečete v levo ali desno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Securities tab"
msgstr "Zavihek vrednostnih papirjev"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>investments view securities tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled naložb, zavihek vrednostnih papirjev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>investments view securities tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled naložb, zavihek vrednostnih papirjev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top of the list of securities is a search box. Because this tab lists "
"all investments you own in all Investment accounts, it can grow lengthy, and "
"you can use the search box to find a specific entry on the list, by typing "
"any part of its name."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu seznama vrednostnih papirjev je iskalno polje. Ker so na tem zavihku "
"navedene vse naložbe, ki jih imate v vseh naložbenih računih, lahko postane "
"daljši in lahko uporabite iskalno polje, da poiščete določen vnos na "
"seznamu, tako da vnesete kateri koli del njegovega imena."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Security</term>"
msgstr "<term>Vrednostni papir</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the security. This column is always displayed. All the other "
"columns are optionally display, as described above. The names should be the "
"same names as shown in the Name column on the Equities tab."
msgstr ""
"Ime vrednostnega papirja. Ta stolpec je vedno prikazan. Vsi drugi stolpci so "
"neobvezno prikazani, kot je opisano zgoraj. Imena morajo biti ista imena, "
"kot so prikazana v stolpcu Ime na zavihku Lastniški kapital."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is trading symbol as used on the market where the equity is traded. It "
"is also the same as the same column in the Equities tab."
msgstr ""
"To je trgovalni simbol, ki se uporablja na trgu, kjer se trguje z lastniškim "
"kapitalom. Prav tako je enak istemu stolpcu na zavihku Lastniški kapital."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the specific type of investment being tracked. Currently, only "
"Stocks, Bonds, and Mutual Funds are possibly values."
msgstr ""
"To je posebna vrsta naložbe, ki se spremlja. Trenutno so možne vrednosti le "
"delnice, obveznice in vzajemni skladi."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Market"
msgstr "Trg"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the market where this investment is traded."
msgstr "To je trg, na katerem se trguje s to naložbo."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Currency"
msgstr "Valuta"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays the symbol of the currency in which this investment is traded."
msgstr "To prikazuje simbol valute, v kateri se trguje s to naložbo."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fraction"
msgstr "Del"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the smallest fraction used when entering the amount of this "
"investment in any transaction."
msgstr ""
"To je najmanjši del, ki se uporablja pri vnosu zneska te naložbe v katero "
"koli transakcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with the Equities tab, the order for any of the columns except Security "
"can changed by left clicking the column header and dragging it to the left "
"or right."
msgstr ""
"Tako kot pri zavihku Lastniški kapital lahko spremenite vrstni red za kateri "
"koli stolpec, razen za vrednostni papir, tako da levo kliknete glavo stolpca "
"in ga povlečete v levo ali desno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating an Investment Account"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje naložbenega računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step on the path to working with investments is to create an "
"Investment account to hold your defined securities. Choose the "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New account...</guimenuitem> menu "
"item to begin the process. Create an account as previously described in the "
"<link linkend=\"details.accounts.create.account\"><guilabel>Account</"
"guilabel></link> section, making sure to choose <quote>Investment</quote> as "
"the type of account."
msgstr ""
"Prvi korak na poti do dela z naložbami je ustvarjanje naložbenega računa za "
"shranjevanje določenih vrednostnih papirjev. Za začetek postopka izberite "
"menijsko postavko <guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov račun...</"
"guimenuitem>. Ustvarite račun, kot je opisano prej v razdelku <link linkend="
"\"details.accounts.create.account\"><guilabel>Račun</guilabel></link>, pri "
"čemer ne pozabite izbrati <quote>Naložba</quote> kot vrsto računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To work with the new investment account, open that account in the Ledgers "
"View, as previously described."
msgstr ""
"Za delo z novim naložbenim računom odprite ta račun v Pogledu glavne knjige, "
"kot je opisano prej."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Price Entry"
msgstr "Vnos cene"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever you enter or edit a buy, sell, or reinvest transaction, you need to "
"specify the number of shares, price per share, and the total amount of the "
"transaction. As described <link linkend=\"details.investments.priceentry"
"\">here</link> you actually specify only two of those values, and &kmymoney; "
"calculates the third. The default price entry setting for new Investment "
"Accounts is <quote>Price per share</quote>, but this can be changed to "
"<quote>Total amount</quote> when you <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit"
"\">edit the account</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli vnesete ali uredite transakcijo nakupa, prodaje ali ponovnega "
"vlaganja, morate določiti število delnic, ceno na delnico in skupni znesek "
"transakcije. Kot je opisano <link linkend=\"details.investments.priceentry"
"\">tukaj</link>, dejansko določite samo dve od teh vrednosti in &kmymoney; "
"izračuna tretjo. Privzeta nastavitev vnosa cene za nove naložbene račune je "
"<quote>Cena na delnico</quote>, vendar jo lahko spremenite v <quote>Skupni "
"znesek</quote>, ko <link linkend=\"details.accounts.edit\"> uredite račun</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Investments to Your Account"
msgstr "Dodajanje naložb na vaš račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add individual securities to your Investment Account, navigate to the "
"<guibutton>Investments</guibutton> View, select the <guibutton>Equities</"
"guibutton> tab, and choose the Investment account where the investment is "
"held from the <guilabel>Select Account</guilabel> dropdown."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati posamezne vrednostne papirje na svoj naložbeni račun, se "
"pomaknite do pogleda <guibutton>Naložbe</guibutton>, izberite zavihek "
"<guibutton>Delnice</guibutton> in izberite naložbeni račun, kjer je naložba, "
"v spustnem meniju <guilabel>Izberi Račun</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-click in any empty space in the view. This brings up the "
"<guimenu>Investment Options</guimenu> context menu. Choose <guimenuitem>New "
"investment...</guimenuitem> from this menu. This launches the <guilabel>New "
"Investment Wizard</guilabel> which you use to create your new Investment."
msgstr ""
"Z desno miškino tipko kliknite kateri koli prazen prostor v pogledu. To "
"prikliče kontekstni meni <guimenu>Naložbene možnosti</guimenu>. V tem meniju "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Nova naložba ...</guimenuitem>. S tem se zažene "
"<guilabel>Čarovnik za novo naložbo</guilabel>, ki ga uporabite za "
"ustvarjanje nove naložbe."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "New Investment Wizard"
msgstr "Čarovnik za nove naložbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first thing you will be asked to enter is the name of the investment. "
"This is the name which will be used on the Equities Tab. You will also be "
"asked to specify the type of investment. The currently available values are "
"Stock, Bond, and Mutual Fund. If your investment is not strictly one of "
"these types, it is ok to mislabel here, as the type is not currently used to "
"restrict or control what you can do with the investment."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar, ki jo boste morali vnesti, je ime naložbe. To je ime, ki bo "
"uporabljeno na zavihku Delnice. Prav tako boste morali določiti vrsto "
"naložbe. Trenutno razpoložljive vrednosti so delnice, obveznice in vzajemni "
"skladi. Če vaša naložba ni strogo ena od teh vrst, je v redu, da tukaj "
"napačno označite, saj se vrsta trenutno ne uporablja za omejevanje ali "
"nadzor nad tem, kaj lahko storite z naložbo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new investment wizard type</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>nove naložbe čarovnik za vrste</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new investment wizard type</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>nove naložbe čarovnik za vrste</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next, the investment details page is presented. The following information is "
"entered on this page:"
msgstr ""
"Nato je predstavljena stran s podrobnostmi o naložbi. Na tej strani so "
"vneseni naslednji podatki:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>new investment wizard details</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>nove naložbe čarovnik za podrobnosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>new investment wizard details</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>nove naložbe čarovnik za podrobnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Trading Symbol. A trading or ticker symbol is an abbreviation used to "
"identify a publicly traded security of a particular instrument on a "
"particular market or exchange. &kmymoney; requires a trading symbol for all "
"securities; however some investments do not have symbols. In this case, you "
"will need to make up a symbol for it."
msgstr ""
"Simbol trgovanja. Simbol trgovanja ali ticker je okrajšava, ki se uporablja "
"za identifikacijo vrednostnega papirja, s katerim se javno trguje, "
"določenega instrumenta na določenem trgu ali borzi. &kmymoney; zahteva "
"trgovalni simbol za vse vrednostne papirje; vendar nekatere naložbe nimajo "
"simbolov. V tem primeru si boste morali izmisliti simbol zanj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The dropdown includes all trading symbols which currently exist in your data "
"file. If you select one of these &kmymoney; will reuse the referenced "
"security for the new equity, unless you check the \"Create duplicates of "
"symbol,\" in which case a new security will be created with the same symbol."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni vključuje vse trgovalne simbole, ki trenutno obstajajo v vaši "
"podatkovni datoteki. Če izberete enega od teh bo &kmymoney; ponovno uporabil "
"referenčni vrednostni papir za nov lastniški kapital, razen če označite "
"\"Ustvari dvojnike simbola\", v tem primeru bo ustvarjen nov vrednostni "
"papir z istim simbolom."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you plan to use <link linkend=\"details.investments.onlinequotes\">Online "
"Quotes</link> to retrieve prices for this investment, ensure that the symbol "
"exactly matches the symbol used by your quote source. Yahoo covers most of "
"the world's markets, and requires a suffix on the end of symbols outside the "
"US, to specify the country or market. For example, Rubicon Limited on the "
"New Zealand market should be entered as <quote>RBC.NZ</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Če nameravate uporabiti <link linkend=\"details.investments.onlinequotes"
"\">Spletne kotacije</link> za pridobivanje cen za to naložbo, zagotovite, da "
"se simbol natančno ujema s simbolom, ki ga uporablja vaš vir ponudb. Yahoo "
"pokriva večino svetovnih trgov in zahteva pripono na koncu simbolov zunaj "
"ZDA za določitev države ali trga. Na primer, Rubicon Limited na "
"novozelandskem trgu je treba vnesti kot <quote>RBC.NZ</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full name of the investment, although it can be a friendly, readable name, "
"&eg;, <quote>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</quote> This name is also referred "
"to as the security."
msgstr ""
"Polno ime naložbe, čeprav je lahko prijazno, berljivo ime &eg; "
"<quote>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</quote> To ime se nanaša tudi na  "
"vrednostni papir."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fraction. This indicates the degree of precision to which your holdings are "
"measured. For example, in the US most mutual funds measure holdings to three "
"decimal places, so you would enter 1000 in this field. Stocks are often "
"measured to only whole units, so you could enter 1 for a stock like this, "
"but you would use 10000 for a stock measured to four decimal digits. You'll "
"want to mirror the same decimal places that your brokerage uses to record "
"your securities so the transactions amounts match within &kmymoney;. Using "
"extra precision will not cause a problem, but using too little precision can "
"cause rounding errors which can make &kmymoney; unable to exactly match the "
"information shown by your brokerage institution."
msgstr ""
"Delež. To označuje stopnjo natančnosti, s katero se meri vaše imetje. Na "
"primer v ZDA večina vzajemnih skladov meri deleže na tri decimalna mesta "
"natančno, zato bi v to polje vnesli 1000. Delnice se pogosto merijo samo na "
"cele enote, zato bi lahko za takšno zalogo vnesli 1, za vrednostne papirje "
"merjene na štiri decimalna mesta, pa bi uporabili 10000. Želeli boste "
"zrcaliti ista decimalna mesta, ki jih vaše posredništvo uporablja za "
"beleženje vaših vrednostnih papirjev, tako da se zneski transakcij ujemajo v "
"&kmymoney;. Uporaba dodatne natančnosti ne bo povzročala težav, vendar pa "
"lahko uporaba premajhne natančnosti povzroči napake pri zaokroževanju, "
"zaradi česar lahko se pri &kmymoney; ne morejo natančno ujemati s podatki, "
"ki jih prikazuje vaša posredniška institucija."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Trading market. Where the investment is traded. This is an optional field "
"which is provided for your convenience. This information is not used "
"anywhere else within &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Trgovanje na trgu. Kjer se trguje z naložbo. To je neobvezno polje, ki je na "
"voljo za vaše udobje. Te informacije se ne uporabljajo nikjer drugje kot "
"znotraj &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Identification number. An optional field to enter additional identification "
"information you might like to keep track of. Stocks often have such a "
"number, which can sometimes be used as well as the symbol for retrieving "
"information about it. Again, this information is not used anywhere else."
msgstr ""
"Identifikacijska številka. Izbirno polje za vnos dodatnih identifikacijskih "
"informacij, ki jih morda želite spremljati. Delnice imajo pogosto takšno "
"številko, ki se lahko včasih uporablja kot simbol za pridobivanje informacij "
"o njih. Še enkrat, te informacije se ne uporabljajo nikjer drugje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Trading currency. The market exchange currency in which this investment is "
"traded. This is typically the currency of the country that the security "
"trades within. It is usually, but not necessarily, the same as the default "
"currency for the Investment account holding that security."
msgstr ""
"Valuta trgovanja. Valuta tržne menjave, v kateri se trguje s to naložbo. To "
"je običajno valuta države, v kateri se trguje z vrednostnim papirjem. "
"Običajno je, vendar ne nujno, enaka privzeti valuti za naložbeni račun, na "
"katerem je ta vrednostni papir."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Price entry. When you enter or edit a buy, sell, or reinvest transaction for "
"this investment, this dropdown indicates whether you want to enter the price "
"per share or the total for all shares or to follow the default for the "
"account, which was specified when the Investment Account was created."
msgstr ""
"Vnos cene. Ko vnesete ali uredite transakcijo nakupa, prodaje ali ponovnega "
"vlaganja za to naložbo, ta spustni meni označuje, ali želite vnesti ceno na "
"delnico ali skupno za vse delnice ali slediti privzeti vrednosti za račun, "
"ki je bila določena, ko je bil Naložbeni račun ustvarjen."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Price Precision. This is a small integer, specifying the number of decimal "
"places used to specify the price of this investment in the specified "
"currency. This is used for both purchase and sale price, the current price, "
"and also for the total value of the investment."
msgstr ""
"Cenovna natančnost. To je majhno celo število, ki določa število decimalnih "
"mest, ki se uporabljajo za določitev cene te naložbe v navedeni valuti. Ta "
"se uporablja za nakupno in prodajno ceno, trenutno ceno in tudi za skupno "
"vrednost naložbe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remainder. This is a dropdown with values Round, Ceil, Floor, and Truncate, "
"which specifies what &kmymoney; should do in the last decimal place of "
"values. For example, this can be relevant when you specify the total price "
"of a purchase rather than an exact price per share."
msgstr ""
"Ostanek. To je spustni meni z vrednostmi Round, Ceil, Floor in Truncate, ki "
"določa funkcijo, kaj naj &kmymoney; naredi na zadnjem decimalnem mestu "
"vrednosti. Na primer, to je lahko pomembno, če navedete skupno ceno nakupa "
"namesto natančne cene na delnico."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you're presented with the Online Update screen. This is where you "
"tell &kmymoney; how you would like to update the prices of your investment, "
"if you do want to use an online source. The following items are set here:"
msgstr ""
"Končno se vam prikaže zaslon za spletno posodobitev. Tukaj rečete &kmymoney; "
"kako želite posodobiti cene svoje naložbe. Tukaj so nastavljeni naslednji "
"elementi:"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:494
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use Finance::Quote. This is an option for &gnucash; users who are used to "
"this style of quotes. Most users can leave this unchecked. Finance::Quote is "
"a Perl module, so to use it, you would need to have both Perl and its "
"Finance::Quote module installed."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite Finance::Quote. To je možnost za uporabnike &gnucash; , ki so "
"vajeni tega sloga kotacij. Večina uporabnikov lahko to možnost pusti "
"neoznačeno. Finance::Quote je modul Perl, zato bi za njegovo uporabo morali "
"imeti nameščen tako Perl kot tudi njegov modul Finance::Quote."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Online Source. The online source you'd like to use for this particular "
"investment. The most common choice is <quote>Yahoo Finance</quote>. Try that "
"first, and if the investment cannot be found using this source, then "
"experiment with the others."
msgstr ""
"Spletni vir. Spletni vir, ki bi ga radi uporabili za to naložbo. "
"Najpogostejša izbira je <quote>Yahoo Finance</quote>. Najprej poskusite s "
"tem in če naložbe ne najdete s tem virom, poskusite z drugim."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that although &kmymoney; knows how to extract security prices from web "
"pages retrieved from Yahoo and many other sources, those sources have been "
"known to change the format of those pages, which can prevent &kmymoney; from "
"successfully extracting the desired information. This is an unfortunately "
"too frequent topic of discussion on the various support channels. However, "
"if fetching prices works for a long time and then you start to get errors, "
"please consider this possibility."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da čeprav &kmymoney; ve, kako pridobiti cene vrednostnih "
"papirjev s spletnih strani, pridobljenih iz Yahooja in številnih drugih "
"virov, znano je, da ti viri spreminjajo format teh strani, kar lahko "
"prepreči &kmymoney; od uspešnega pridobivanja želenih informacij. To je žal "
"prepogosta tema razprav na različnih podpornih kanalih. Če pa pridobivanje "
"cen deluje že dlje časa in se vam potem začnejo pojavljati napake, "
"razmislite o tej možnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Factor. A multiplier that should be applied to quotes retrieved for this "
"investment. This is most commonly needed for UK stocks where the price "
"quoted is in pence (1/100), and the stock is denominated in pounds. In this "
"case, enter 0,01 for the Factor."
msgstr ""
"Faktor. Množitelj, ki ga je treba uporabiti za ponudbe, pridobljene za to "
"naložbo. To je najpogosteje potrebno za delnice v Združenem kraljestvu, kjer "
"je navedena cena v penijih (1/100), delnica pa je denominirana v funtih. V "
"tem primeru za faktor vnesite 0,01."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using a Security in more than one Investment Account"
msgstr "Uporaba vrednostnega papirja na več kot enem naložbenem računu"

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Caution"
msgstr "Previdnost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to own shares of the same security in more than one "
"investment account, such as a regular investment account and also a "
"retirement account. In previous versions of &kmymoney; it was easy to "
"unintentionally have &kmymoney; treat them as if each of the securities was "
"a different underlying investment. That often caused confusion, as well as "
"duplicate storage, such as having two copies of the entire price history of "
"the equity. Currently, it is much easier to avoid this situation, but it is "
"important to pay attention when creating new equities within an Investment "
"Account."
msgstr ""
"Delnice istega vrednostnega papirja je mogoče imeti v lasti na več kot enem "
"naložbenem računu, na primer na običajnem naložbenem računu in tudi na "
"pokojninskem računu. V prejšnjih različicah &kmymoney; jih je bilo enostavno "
"nenamerno imeti v &kmymoney; in obravnavati, kot da bi bil vsak vrednostni "
"papir drugačna osnovna naložba. To je pogosto povzročalo zmedo, pa tudi "
"podvojeno shranjevanje, na primer dve kopiji celotne zgodovine cen "
"lastniškega kapitala. Trenutno se je veliko lažje izogniti tej situaciji, "
"vendar je pomembno, da ste pozorni pri ustvarjanju novih delnic znotraj "
"naložbenega računa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you add a security to an investment account, and that investment "
"already exists in another investment account, you need to be careful if you "
"want to reuse it rather than creating a new, duplicate entry. In the "
"<guilabel>New Investment Wizard</guilabel>, after selecting the name and "
"type of investment and clicking <guibutton>Next</guibutton>, when you select "
"an existing <guilabel>Trading Symbol</guilabel> some of the other fields on "
"the form will be filled in with the relevant information from the existing "
"security, and the existing security will be used unless you select the "
"\"Create duplicate of symbol\" checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Ko dodate vrednostni papir na naložbeni račun in ta naložba že obstaja na "
"drugem naložbenem računu, morate biti previdni, če ga želite znova "
"uporabiti, namesto da ustvarite nov, podvojen vnos. Ko v <guilabel>čarovniku "
"za nove naložbe</guilabel> izberete ime in vrsto naložbe ter kliknete "
"<guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>, ko izberete obstoječi <guilabel>trgovalni "
"simbol</guilabel> bo nekaj drugih polj na obrazcu izpolnjenih z ustreznimi "
"informacijami iz obstoječega vrednostnega papirja in uporabljen bo obstoječi "
"vrednostni papir, razen če izberete potrditveno polje »Ustvari dvojnik "
"simbola«."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing an Investment"
msgstr "Urejanje naložbe"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Equities</guilabel> tab of the Investments View lists your "
"current holdings in this Investment account. Right-click any of the "
"investments to bring up the <guimenu>Investment Options</guimenu> context "
"menu, where you can add, edit, or delete an individual investment from this "
"account. Also, you can update the price of an investments here either "
"manually or via its online source. In addition, it is possible to close an "
"empty account, or to reopen a closed account."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Delnice</guilabel> v pogledu naložb navaja vaše trenutne "
"delnice na tem naložbenem računu. Z desno miškino tipko kliknite katero koli "
"od naložb, da prikažete kontekstni meni <guimenu>Naložbene možnosti</"
"guimenu>, kjer lahko dodate, uredite ali izbrišete posamezno naložbo iz tega "
"računa. Prav tako lahko tu posodobite ceno naložbe ročno ali prek spletnega "
"vira. Poleg tega je mogoče zapreti prazen račun ali ponovno odpreti zaprt "
"račun."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose to Edit an Investment, you will use the <guilabel>Investment "
"detail wizard</guilabel>, which looks and functions just like the "
"<guilabel>New Investment Wizard</guilabel>, as described in the previous "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Če se odločite za urejanje naložbe, boste uporabili <guilabel>Čarovnika za "
"podrobnosti o naložbi</guilabel>, ki je videti in deluje tako kot "
"<guilabel>Čarovnik za nove naložbe</guilabel>, kot je opisano v prejšnjem "
"razdelku."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Right-clicking an entry in the Securities tab produces a "
"<guilabel>Securities Options</guilabel> context menu, where you can edit or "
"delete a security. Actually creating a security is done when you create an "
"equity in an Investment account, and do not choose to reuse an existing "
"security, as discussed above."
msgstr ""
"Z desnim klikom na vnos na zavihku Vrednostni papirji se odpre kontekstni "
"meni <guilabel>Možnosti vrednostnih papirjev</guilabel>, kjer lahko uredite "
"ali izbrišete vrednostni papir. Pravzaprav se vrednostni papir ustvari, ko "
"ustvarite lastniški kapital na naložbenem računu in se ne odločite za "
"ponovno uporabo obstoječega vrednostnega papirja, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Investment Transactions"
msgstr "Naložbene transakcije"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>investment transaction form</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>obrazec za investicijsko transakcijo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>investment transaction form</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>obrazec za investicijsko transakcijo</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Investment transactions are entered and edited in the <link linkend="
"\"details.ledgers\">Ledgers</link> view, as with transactions in other types "
"of accounts. However, the fields shown will be different, and vary depending "
"on the activity or transaction type. Investment transactions have some "
"additional elements, described below."
msgstr ""
"Naložbene transakcije se vnašajo in urejajo v pogledu <link linkend="
"\"details.ledgers\">Glavne knjige</link>, tako kot pri transakcijah v drugih "
"vrstah računov. Vendar se bodo prikazana polja razlikovala in se bodo "
"razlikovala glede na vrsto dejavnosti ali transakcije. Naložbene transakcije "
"imajo nekaj dodatnih elementov, opisanih spodaj."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activity"
msgstr "Dejavnost"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Activity for an investment transaction describes what type of action is "
"happening to the security. The following activities are supported:"
msgstr ""
"Dejavnost za naložbeno transakcijo opisuje vrsto dejanja, ki se dogaja z "
"vrednostnim papirjem. Podprte so naslednje dejavnosti:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buy/Sell"
msgstr "Nakup/Prodaja"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use to record the purchase or sale of an individual security. This action "
"requires an account to transfer the funds from/to, which defaults to the "
"Brokerage account, if one has been defined for this Investment account."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite za beleženje nakupa ali prodaje posameznega vrednostnega papirja. "
"To dejanje zahteva račun za prenos sredstev iz/na, ki je privzeto na "
"posredniški račun, če je bil določen za ta naložbeni račun."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dividend/Yield/Interest Income"
msgstr "Dividende/donos/dohodki od obresti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also known as a <quote>Cash Dividend,</quote> this action is used when you "
"receive an interest or dividend disbursement of cash from your security. "
"This action also requires an account to transfer the funds to. The three "
"terms are used interchangeably."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje, znano tudi kot <quote>denarna dividenda</quote>, se uporabi, ko "
"prejmete izplačilo obresti ali dividende v gotovini od svojega vrednostnega "
"papirja. To dejanje zahteva tudi račun za prenos sredstev. Ti trije izrazi "
"se uporabljajo zamenljivo."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reinvest dividend"
msgstr "Reinvestiraj dividende"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a dividend where the proceeds are used to purchase additional shares "
"of the security."
msgstr ""
"To je dividenda, pri kateri se izkupiček uporabi za nakup dodatnih delnic "
"vrednostnega papirja."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add/Remove shares"
msgstr "Dodaj/odstrani delnice"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A simple increase or decrease in the number of shares you own. This should "
"be used very rarely, because it's uncommon for shares to just show up in "
"your account (or to disappear) unless it's a purchase, sale, or dividend "
"reinvestment. One use of these activities is for some situations &kmymoney; "
"does not natively handle, such as the exchange of some number of shares of a "
"security for a different number of shares of a different security or "
"different class of the same security."
msgstr ""
"Preprosto povečanje ali zmanjšanje števila delnic, ki jih imate. To je treba "
"uporabljati zelo redko, ker je neobičajno, da se delnice kar prikažejo v "
"vašem računu (ali izginejo), razen če gre za nakup, prodajo ali ponovno "
"vlaganje dividend. Ena uporaba teh dejavnosti je v nekaterih situacijah, ki "
"jih &kmymoney; izvorno ne obravnava, kot je zamenjava določenega števila "
"delnic vrednostnega papirja za različno število delnic drugega vrednostnega "
"papirja ali drugega razreda istega vrednostnega papirja."

#. Tag: term
#: details-investments.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split shares"
msgstr "Razcepi delnice"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used when the stock is split. Enter the ratio of the split in the "
"<quote>Split Ratio</quote> field. For example, in a 3:2 split, enter 1.5. "
"Reverse splits, where the ratio is less than one, such as 2:3, although "
"uncommon, are also allowed."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja, ko je delnica razdeljena. Vnesite razmerje delitve v polje "
"<quote>Razmerje delitve</quote>. Na primer, pri delitvi 3:2 vnesite 1,5. "
"Dovoljene so tudi obratne delitve, kjer je razmerje manjše od ena, na primer "
"2:3, čeprav so redke."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Security</title>"
msgstr "<title>Vrednostni papir</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each investment transaction must be associated with an individual security. "
"The dropdown shows all securities you own in the current Investment account "
"- select the one for this transaction."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka naložbena transakcija mora biti povezana s posameznim vrednostnim "
"papirjem. Spustni meni prikazuje vse vrednostne papirje, ki jih imate na "
"trenutnem naložbenem računu - izberite tistega za to transakcijo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For any transaction which generates or requires money, you must enter the "
"account where the money is transferred to/from. If your investment account "
"has an associated Brokerage account, it is usually best to transfer the "
"funds there. This applies to funds for purchase or sale of the security, as "
"well as for fees paid or interest or dividends earned."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako transakcijo, ki ustvarja ali zahteva denar, morate vnesti račun, na "
"katerega je denar nakazan/iz katerega je nakazan. Če ima vaš naložbeni račun "
"povezan posredniški račun, je običajno najbolje, da sredstva prenesete tja. "
"To velja za sredstva za nakup ali prodajo vrednostnega papirja, kot tudi za "
"plačane provizije ali zaslužene obresti ali dividende."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:691
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shares, Price &amp; Total Amount"
msgstr "Delnice, cena &amp; Skupni znesek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For buy, sell, and reinvestment transactions, the number of shares, the "
"price per share, and the total amount of the transaction must be "
"established. You can enter any two of these, and &kmymoney; will calculate "
"the third. It is usually best to enter just the total amount and the number "
"of shares, because these are the known facts of the transaction. &kmymoney; "
"will automatically calculate the price per share. Note that there is only "
"one entry field for the price, and it will be labeled <quote>Transaction "
"amount</quote> or <quote>Price/share</quote> depending on the setting of the "
"<guilabel>Price entry</guilabel> option when the investment was <link "
"linkend=\"details.investments.newinvestmentwizard\">set up</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za transakcije nakupa, prodaje in ponovnega vlaganja je treba določiti "
"število delnic, ceno na delnico in skupni znesek transakcije. Vnesete lahko "
"katera koli dva od teh in &kmymoney; bo izračunal tretjega. Običajno je "
"najbolje vnesti samo skupni znesek in število delnic, ker so to znana "
"dejstva transakcije. &kmymoney; samodejno izračuna ceno delnice. "
"Upoštevajte, da obstaja samo eno vnosno polje za ceno in bo označeno z "
"<quote>Znesek transakcije</quote> ali <quote>Cena za delnico</quote>, "
"odvisno od nastavitve <guilabel>Vnos cene</guilabel>, ko je bila naložba "
"<link linkend=\"details.investments.newinvestmentwizard\">nastavljena</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fees"
msgstr "Pristojbine"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With many investment transactions you can include the fees (or commission) "
"you paid the broker. If you enter a category for the fee, then a field will "
"be shown to the right where you can enter the amount of the fee. If you need "
"to enter more than one fee for the transaction, you can use the <link "
"linkend=\"details.ledgers.split\">Split Transactions</link> feature. In this "
"case, when you complete entering all the splits, the total amount of the "
"fees will be shown to the right."
msgstr ""
"Pri številnih naložbenih transakcijah lahko vključite nadomestila (ali "
"provizije), ki ste jih plačali posredniku. Če vnesete kategorijo za "
"pristojbino, se bo na desni strani prikazalo polje, kjer lahko vnesete "
"znesek pristojbine. Če morate za transakcijo vnesti več kot eno provizijo, "
"lahko uporabite funkcijo <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split\">Razcepljene "
"transakcije</link>. V tem primeru, ko zaključite z vnosom vseh delitev, bo "
"na desni prikazan skupni znesek provizij."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interest"
msgstr "Obresti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is how you enter an interest or dividend payment from a security. As "
"with fees, if you enter a category, then a field will be shown to the right "
"where you can enter the amount. You can also use the split transaction "
"feature, if required."
msgstr ""
"Tako vnesete plačilo obresti ali dividend iz vrednostnega papirja. Tako kot "
"pri provizijah se bo, če vnesete kategorijo, na desni strani prikazalo "
"polje, kjer lahko vnesete znesek. Po potrebi lahko uporabite tudi funkcijo "
"razdeljene transakcije."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working With Foreign Investments"
msgstr "Delo s tujimi naložbami"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:727
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; supports multiple currencies, and there are situations where this "
"can be very useful, if not essential. However, doing so requires extra care "
"to assure accurate records. As noted above, when you add a security, you "
"must specify its trading currency. This might not be the same as the base "
"currency for your &kmymoney; file, and it also might not be the same as the "
"base currency for the investment account in which you hold the security or "
"for the account where you transfer your funds to/from for buys/sells/"
"dividends."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; podpira več valut in obstajajo situacije, ko je to lahko zelo "
"koristno, če ne nujno. Vendar pa je pri tem potrebna posebna pozornost, da "
"se zagotovijo točni zapisi. Kot je navedeno zgoraj, morate, ko dodate "
"vrednostni papir, določiti njegovo trgovalno valuto. To morda ni isto kot "
"osnovna valuta za vaš &kmymoney; in morda tudi ni enaka osnovni valuti za "
"naložbeni račun, na katerem imate vrednostni papir, ali za račun, na "
"katerega/iz katerega prenašate sredstva za nakupe/prodaje/dividende."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Consider a hypothetical case, where your base currency is USD. You have an "
"investment account in EUR, and a brokerage account also in EUR. In that "
"investment account, you hold shares of TietoEnator, which is traded in SEK."
msgstr ""
"Razmislite o hipotetičnem primeru, kjer je vaša osnovna valuta USD. "
"Naložbeni račun imate v EUR, posredniški račun pa prav tako v EUR. Na tem "
"naložbenem računu imate delnice družbe TietoEnator, s katerimi se trguje v "
"SEK."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you enter a buy transaction for this investment, use SEK as the "
"currency. So if you buy 100 shares at a price of SEK 248.00, for a total of "
"SEK 24,800.00, enter these values in the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Ko vnesete nakupno transakcijo za to naložbo, uporabite SEK kot valuto. Če "
"torej kupite 100 delnic po ceni 248,00 SEK, za skupno 24.800,00 SEK, te "
"vrednosti vnesite v transakcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose the brokerage account to fund the transfer, you'll be warned "
"that it's in a different currency."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete posredniški račun za financiranje nakazila, boste opozorjeni, da "
"je v drugi valuti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>investment transaction currency warning</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>opozorilo o valuti naložbene transakcije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>investment transaction currency warning</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>opozorilo o valuti naložbene transakcije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you finish entering the transaction, you will be prompted for a price "
"update to the investment account's currency, in this case, SEK -> EUR. "
"Review the documentation on <link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices"
"\">Entering Prices Manually</link> for more information on the price dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z vnosom transakcije, boste pozvani k posodobitvi cene v valuti "
"naložbenega računa, v tem primeru SEK -> EUR. Preglejte dokumentacijo o "
"<link linkend=\"details.currencies.prices\">Ročnem vnašanju cen</link> za "
"več informacij o pogovornem oknu s cenami."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>exchange rate editor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>urejevalnik menjalnih tečajev</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>exchange rate editor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>urejevalnik menjalnih tečajev</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you then switch over to the brokerage account, you will see the "
"transaction as EUR 2,254.54, assuming an exchange rate is 11.0000 SEK/EUR."
msgstr ""
"Če nato preklopite na posredniški račun, boste videli transakcijo kot "
"2.254,54 EUR, ob predpostavki, da je menjalni tečaj 11,0000 SEK/EUR."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updating Security Prices"
msgstr "Posodabljanje cen vrednostnih papirjev"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways of updating the prices for your investments. You can "
"either enter the price manually or have &kmymoney; fetch it from the web."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva načina za posodobitev cen za vaše naložbe. Ceno lahko vnesete "
"ročno ali pa imate &kmymoney; prenos s spleta."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manual Price Updates"
msgstr "Ročne posodobitve cen"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter prices for your investments using the same <link linkend="
"\"details.currencies.prices\">Price Editor</link> as used for currencies."
msgstr ""
"Cene za svoje naložbe lahko vnesete z istim <link linkend=\"details."
"currencies.prices\">urejevalnikom cen</link>, kot se uporablja za valute."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Price Quotes"
msgstr "Spletne kotacije cen"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:805
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has the ability to download the latest prices for your securities "
"and currencies via the web."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ima možnost prenosa najnovejših cen za vaše vrednostne papirje in "
"valute prek spleta."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid "How Online Quotes Work"
msgstr "Kako delujejo spletne kotacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At your request, &kmymoney; will fetch a page from the web that contains the "
"latest price for each security. By default, prices are fetched from <ulink "
"url=\"https://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>, and are subject "
"to the terms and conditions of that site."
msgstr ""
"Na vašo zahtevo &kmymoney; bo iz spleta pridobil stran, ki vsebuje "
"najnovejšo ceno za vsak vrednostni papir. Cene so privzeto pridobljene iz "
"<ulink url=\"https://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink> in zanje "
"veljajo pogoji in določila tega mesta."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The online quote lookup uses the security's trading symbol to find the "
"price. Therefore, it is important to set the symbol correctly. Yahoo "
"supports stocks from most major world markets, so it is usually just a "
"matter of finding the correct symbol. For example, TietoEnator trades on the "
"Stockholm Stock Exchange market, and its Yahoo symbol is TIEN.ST."
msgstr ""
"Spletno iskanje kotacij uporablja trgovalni simbol vrednostnega papirja za "
"iskanje cene. Zato je pomembno, da simbol pravilno nastavite. Yahoo podpira "
"delnice z večine večjih svetovnih trgov, zato je običajno le treba najti "
"pravi simbol. Na primer, TietoEnator trguje na Stockholmski borzi, njegov "
"Yahoo simbol pa je TIEN.ST."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To find the trading symbol for a security supported by Yahoo, use the "
"<quote>Symbol Lookup</quote> feature at <ulink url=\"https://finance.yahoo."
"com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>. You should have set the trading symbol when "
"initially entering the security into &kmymoney;."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati trgovalni simbol za vrednostni papir, ki ga podpira "
"Yahoo, uporabite funkcijo <quote>Symbol Lookup</quote> na <ulink url="
"\"https://finance.yahoo.com\">finance.yahoo.com</ulink>. Ob prvem vnosu "
"vrednostnega papirja v &kmymoney; bi morali nastaviti simbol trgovanja."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assigning a Quote Source"
msgstr "Dodeljevanje vira kotacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In order to get online price quotes, you first have to enable the feature "
"for each security or currency you want updated, by setting an <quote>Online "
"Quote Source</quote>. This is the name of the service from which the quote "
"should be fetched. &kmymoney; ships with several sources to choose from. "
"Yahoo is the recommended default source, and should work for most "
"investments and all currencies."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pridobiti spletne kotacije cen, morate najprej omogočiti funkcijo "
"za vsak vrednostni papir ali valuto, ki jo želite posodobiti, tako da "
"nastavite <quote>Spletni vir kotacij</quote>. To je ime storitve, iz katere "
"je treba pridobiti kotacijo. &kmymoney; ponuja več virov, med katerimi lahko "
"izbirate. Yahoo je priporočen privzeti vir in bi moral delovati za večino "
"naložb in vse valute."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:844
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To assign a quote source for an investment, navigate to the investment "
"summary view for the account in which the security is held. Edit the "
"security by right-clicking it and selecting <guimenuitem>Edit Investment ..."
"</guimenuitem>. In the Investment Detail Wizard, click <guibutton>Next</"
"guibutton> twice, for the Online Update section. In the Online source "
"dropdown box, select the online source for your needs."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodeliti vir kotacije za naložbo, se pomaknite do pogleda povzetka "
"naložbe za račun, v katerem je vrednostni papir. Uredite vrednostni papir "
"tako, da ga kliknete z desno tipko miške in izberete <guimenuitem>Uredi "
"naložbo...</guimenuitem>. V čarovniku za podrobnosti naložbe dvakrat "
"kliknite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton> za razdelek Spletna posodobitev. V "
"spustnem polju Spletni vir izberite spletni vir za svoje potrebe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Versions of &kmymoney; starting with 0.9 contain support for the Perl "
"Finance::Quote package for obtaining online quotes. This is intended "
"primarily as a convenience for those users converting from the &gnucash; "
"finance package, which uses it as its native method. If you do select this "
"option, you should see a different list of sources, those supported by "
"Finance::Quote. If the list is empty, it suggests that the package is not "
"properly installed. See their web site at <ulink url=\"http://finance-quote."
"sourceforge.net\"> http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net</ulink> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Različice &kmymoney; od 0.9 naprej vsebujejo podporo za paket Finance::Quote "
"za pridobivanje spletnih kotacij. To je mišljeno predvsem kot priročnost za "
"tiste uporabnike, ki pretvarjajo iz &gnucash; finančni paket, ki ga "
"uporablja kot domačo metodo. Če izberete to možnost, bi morali videti drug "
"seznam virov, tistih, ki jih podpira Finance::Quote. Če je seznam prazen, to "
"pomeni, da paket ni pravilno nameščen. Za več informacij si oglejte njihovo "
"spletno mesto na <ulink url=\"http://finance-quote.sourceforge.net\"> http://"
"finance-quote.sourceforge.net</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjusting a quote"
msgstr "Prilagoditev kotacije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some online sources do not report the price in a base quantity (&eg;, EUR) "
"but in a fraction (&eg;, Cent). Using this information for a price will "
"produce wrong values for your investments."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri spletni viri ne poročajo o ceni v osnovni količini (&eg; EUR), "
"temveč v delčku (&eg; Cent). Uporaba teh informacij za ceno bo ustvarila "
"napačne vrednosti za vaše naložbe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is the case for your online source, you can use the "
"<guilabel>Factor</guilabel> field to enter an adjusting factor. For the "
"above mentioned example the factor would be 0.01."
msgstr ""
"Če to velja za vaš spletni vir, lahko uporabite polje <guilabel>Faktor</"
"guilabel>, da vnesete prilagoditveni faktor. Za zgoraj navedeni primer bi "
"bil faktor 0,01."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Factor</guilabel> field is only available if a "
"<guibutton>Quote Source</guibutton> has been selected."
msgstr ""
"Polje <guilabel>Faktor</guilabel> je na voljo le, če je bil izbran "
"<guibutton>Vir ponudbe</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fetching Quotes"
msgstr "Pridobivanje kotacij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Typically, you will update the prices for all your securities and currencies "
"as a single operation. Choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Update Stock and Currency Prices...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item to bring up the online price quotes dialog. Press "
"<guibutton>Update All</guibutton> to fetch quotes for all securities and "
"currencies in your &kmymoney; file."
msgstr ""
"Običajno posodobite cene za vse svoje vrednostne papirje in valute kot eno "
"samo operacijo. Izberite element menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi cene delnic in valut...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno s spletnimi kotacijami cen. "
"Pritisnite <guibutton>Posodobi vse</guibutton>, da pridobite kotacije za vse "
"vrednostne papirje in valute v vaši datoteki &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-investments.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid "online update stock and currency prices"
msgstr "spletno posodabljanje cen delnic in valut"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-investments.docbook:901
#, no-c-format
msgid "online update stock and currency price"
msgstr "posodobi cene delnic in valut"

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding or Editing Quote Sources"
msgstr "Dodajanje ali urejanje virov kotacij"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adding or editing quote sources is not recommended for anyone but the most "
"technical user. You should feel comfortable reading HTML and writing complex "
"regular expressions. If this doesn't sound like you, please use one of the "
"<link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">suggested support channels</link> if you "
"are having problems with a particular source or if none of the quote sources "
"work for you. If looking for a source for prices for a security not found by "
"one of the existing sources, ideally, please point us to a web page where "
"these prices can be obtained. Additionally you can consult with members of "
"the KDE Community Forum for &kmymoney; as they may already have a solution "
"available for your needs."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje ali urejanje virov kotacij ni priporočljivo za nikogar, razen za "
"najbolj tehnične uporabnike. Morali bi se počutiti udobno pri branju HTML in "
"pisanju zapletenih regularnih izrazov. Če vam to ne ugaja, uporabite enega "
"od <link linkend=\"firsttime.contact\">predlaganih kanalov za podporo</"
"link>, če imate težave z določenim virom ali če vam nobeden od virov kotacij "
"ne ustreza . Če iščete vir za cene za vrednostni papir, ki ga ne najde noben "
"od obstoječih virov, nas v idealnem primeru usmerite na spletno stran, kjer "
"lahko dobite te cene. Poleg tega se lahko posvetujete s člani foruma "
"skupnosti KDE za &kmymoney; ker morda že imajo na voljo rešitev za vaše "
"potrebe."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do feel up to the challenge, here's how it works. The quote sources "
"are contained in the settings dialog. Choose the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmymoney;</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. From there, choose the <guilabel>Online "
"Quotes</guilabel> section. You can choose an existing source to edit, or "
"create a new one. When you are done with your changes, be sure to press the "
"<guibutton>Update</guibutton> button before exiting the dialog. Your changes "
"are not saved by default."
msgstr ""
"Če se počutite kos izzivu, to deluje tako. Viri kotacij so v pogovornem oknu "
"z nastavitvami. Izberite menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmymoney;</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Od "
"tam izberite razdelek <guilabel>Spletne kotacije</guilabel>. Za urejanje "
"lahko izberete obstoječi vir ali ustvarite novega. Ko končate s spremembami, "
"ne pozabite pritisniti gumb <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton>, preden "
"zapustite pogovorno okno. Vaše spremembe privzeto niso shranjene."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first thing to consider in an online quote source is the URL. This is "
"the page that is fetched from the web. You will see a %1 in all sources, and "
"a %2 in currency sources. For investments, %1 is replaced by the trading "
"symbol. For currencies, %1 is replaced by the From currency, and %2 is "
"replaced by the To currency. This URL is then fetched, all HTML tags are "
"(optionally) removed, and that stripped file is then sent to the page parser."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar, ki jo morate upoštevati pri spletnem viru kotacij, je URL. To je "
"stran, ki je pridobljena iz spleta. V vseh virih boste videli %1, v valutnih "
"virih pa %2. Pri naložbah se %1 nadomesti s simbolom trgovanja. Pri valutah "
"se %1 nadomesti z valuto Od, %2 pa z valuto Za. Ta URL se nato pridobi, vse "
"oznake HTML se (izbirno) odstranijo in ta odstranjena datoteka se nato "
"pošlje razčlenjevalniku strani."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the URL can also be a file: URL, which the quote fetcher takes to "
"be the path to an executable script. It will pass any command-line arguments "
"to it that you have specified, and feed the stdout of that script to the "
"page parser. For example, you might have a script called getquote.sh that "
"contains custom quote logic, taking the symbol as a single parameter. Your "
"URL would be <quote>file:/path/to/getquote.sh %1</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je URL lahko tudi datoteka: URL, ki ga iskalnik kotacij "
"obravnava kot pot do izvršljivega skripta. Predal mu bo vse argumente ukazne "
"vrstice, ki ste jih določili, in posredoval stdout tega skripta "
"razčlenjevalniku strani. Na primer, lahko imate skript z imenom getquote.sh, "
"ki vsebuje logiko narekovajev po meri, pri čemer simbol vzame kot en sam "
"parameter. Vaš URL bi bil <quote>file:/path/to/getquote.sh %1</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page parser looks for a symbol, a date, and a price. Regular expressions "
"tell it how to extract those items from the page. Please review the "
"documentation for the <ulink url=\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression."
"html\">QRegularExpression class</ulink> for the exact syntax regular "
"expressions used by &kmymoney;. There should be exactly one capture "
"expression, surrounded by parentheses, in each regexp field. The date format "
"further tells the date parser the order of year, month, and day. This date "
"format should always be in the form \"%x %x %x\". where x is y, m, or d. The "
"date parser is very smart. <quote>%m %d %y</quote> will parse "
"<quote>December 31st, 2005</quote> as easily as <quote>12/31/05</quote>. Two "
"digit years are interpreted as being in the range of 1950-2049."
msgstr ""
"Razčlenjevalnik strani išče simbol, datum in ceno. Regularni izrazi povedo, "
"kako izvleči te elemente s strani. Preglejte dokumentacijo za <ulink url="
"\"https://doc.qt.io/qt-5/qregularexpression.html\">razred "
"QRegularExpression</ulink> za natančno sintakso regularnih izrazov, ki jih "
"uporablja &kmymoney;. V vsakem polju regularnega izraza mora biti natanko en "
"izraz za zajemanje, obdan z oklepaji. Format datuma razčlenjevalniku datuma "
"nadalje pove vrstni red leta, meseca in dneva. Ta oblika datuma mora biti "
"vedno v obliki \"%x %x %x\". kjer je x y, m ali d. Razčlenjevalnik datumov "
"je zelo pameten. <quote>%m %d %y</quote> bo razčlenil <quote>31. december "
"2005</quote> tako enostavno kot <quote>31.12.05</quote>. Dvomestna leta se "
"razlagajo kot v razponu od 1950 do 2049."

#. Tag: title
#: details-investments.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unimplemented Features"
msgstr "Neimplementirane zmožnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are some features that are normally associated with investments which "
"are not yet implemented in &kmymoney;. These include, but are not limited to "
"derivatives, options, and futures. In addition, when you sell a security, "
"&kmymoney; does not know which specific shares you are selling, &ie;, the "
"oldest or the most recently purchased, so it cannot calculate return on "
"investment. Finally, it has no direct knowledge about any country's specific "
"tax reporting requirements, although these can usually be handled by marking "
"as Tax related all the categories you use for transactions which might have "
"tax consequences."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere funkcije, ki so običajno povezane z naložbami, še niso "
"implementirane v &kmymoney;. Ti vključujejo, vendar niso omejeni na izvedene "
"finančne instrumente, opcije in terminske pogodbe. Poleg tega, ko prodate "
"vrednostni papir, &kmymoney; ne ve, katere konkretne delnice prodajate, tj. "
"najstarejše ali nazadnje kupljene, zato ne more izračunati donosnosti "
"naložbe. Nazadnje nima neposrednega znanja o posebnih zahtevah glede "
"davčnega poročanja v kateri koli državi, čeprav jih je običajno mogoče "
"obravnavati tako, da vse kategorije, ki jih uporabljate za transakcije, ki "
"bi lahko imele davčne posledice, označite kot povezane z davki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-investments.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kmymoney; development team is aware of these and additional issues, and "
"has been collecting requirements and notes for an eventual major re-write of "
"how the program handles investments. When that process begins (there is no "
"current schedule) there will be an opportunity for users to provide input on "
"any additional needs and desires in this area."
msgstr ""
"Razvojna ekipa &kmymoney; se zaveda teh in dodatnih težav in je zbirala "
"zahteve in opombe za morebitno večjo prenovo tega, kako program obravnava "
"naložbe. Ko se bo ta proces začel (trenutno časovnega plana še ni), bodo "
"imeli uporabniki priložnost, da posredujejo svoje podatke o dodatnih "
"potrebah in željah na tem področju."

